      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait r u sure? i get really bad cramps every month and they feel exactly like this. i'm also feeling super bloated. it seems a bit extreme to go to the ER just for cramps lol. if i just take a really high dose of ibuprofen, like 800mg or something, wouldn't that just help the inflammation and let me sleep? i really dont want to deal with a hospital visit tonight if i can help it.",
